'''Haynes''' was a member of the crew of [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Scarlet Bloodhawk]]'s ship, the ''[[Capri Nitari]]''. Along with [[Shandar (smuggler)|Shandar]], the three two were known to have made the [[Kessel Run/Legends|Kessel Run]] at least once, and spent some time bar-hopping afterward on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Mandrine/Legends|Mandrine]], where Haynes frequented a bar called [[Maizie's]].

